{"tid":935341,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"袋鼠Roger死左.....","createTime":"2018-12-10T02:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T12:11:07.000Z","uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45abbb41c640e379dfaf970e95dd14fbebe440b9","tid":935341,"uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"徒手壓扁鐵桶爆紅　袋鼠界阿諾舒華辛力加離世　「媽媽」悲痛<br />\n<br />\n澳洲一隻名叫羅傑（Roger）的袋鼠渾身長滿結實的肌肉，2015年憑一張徒手壓扁鐵桶的照片在網上爆紅，被稱為「袋鼠界阿諾舒華辛力加」。然而，牠的飼養員巴恩斯（Chris Barnes）周六（8日）在Facebook悲傷地宣布：羅傑已經離世，終年12歲。<br />\n<br />\n[url<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/269061/徒手壓扁鐵桶爆紅-袋鼠界阿諾舒華辛力加離世-媽媽-悲痛][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F269061%2F%E5%BE%92%E6%89%8B%E5%A3%93%E6%89%81%E9%90%B5%E6%A1%B6%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E8%A2%8B%E9%BC%A0%E7%95%8C%E9%98%BF%E8%AB%BE%E8%88%92%E8%8F%AF%E8%BE%9B%E5%8A%9B%E5%8A%A0%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD-%E6%82%B2%E7%97%9B%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=VfU7UGqeyHdBUD1vc26Tcf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a4bc7c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/269061/徒手壓扁鐵桶爆紅-袋鼠界阿諾舒華辛力加離世-媽媽-悲痛][/url]</a> source <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/10/104745_2098bdf21e93f64a01fab1793112f83a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F10%2F104745_2098bdf21e93f64a01fab1793112f83a.png&h=0cfc82a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b019d43bb8e7833e524863320e622d3b62cb52b7","tid":935341,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}